@EU_Commission @Transport_EU @EBrivioEU @Bulc_EU Think about All the citizens in europe ... 
Some of them, need day light savings, in order to duly and fully work, study, and spend time with their family, during the day. Not at night!
Its not about the Numbers ... Its about the people and the way we live our lives

@EU_Commission @Transport_EU @EBrivioEU @Bulc_EU Apart from the server being STILL down (better luck with the satellites, guys) should we be worried by this:
" whereas it is crucial to maintain a unified EU time regime even after the end of biannual time changes"
Apart from keeping EUrocrats happy, why is this crucial?

@EU_Commission @Transport_EU @EBrivioEU @Bulc_EU Server still down, but I prefer summertime all year, too. Winter time is even worse in winter.

#summertime
